data.enText: having a light colour, between yellow and red

tr: resembling or containing or abounding in sand

value.def: A sandy area is covered with sand.
Sandy hair is light orangey-brown in colour.
value.tran: （头发）沙土色的，浅黄褐色的，浅棕色的
